OL,3,CHow a family fell foul of travel
OL,4,Cinsurance rules and now face a huge
OL,5,Cbill
OL,7,FWhen three generations of the Kirby
OL,8,FWhitemore family packed their bags for
OL,9,FZante last month, they thought they
OL,10,Fhad everything they needed: suncream,
OL,11,Fsnorkel, flippers, everything to enjoy
OL,12,Fa week on the Greek island. They had
OL,13,Feven remembered to buy travel
OL,14,Finsurance.
