OL,3,CHow a family fell foul of travel
OL,4,Cinsurance rules and now face a huge
OL,5,Cbill
OL,7,FToday, that dream vacation has become
OL,8,Fa living nightmare, with 67-year-old
OL,9,FAlan Kirby fighting for his life in an
OL,10,FAthens hospital while his devastated
OL,11,Ffamily faces an impossible choice
OL,12,Fbetween staying by his side and
OL,13,Ffinancial ruin.
OL,15,FThe holiday began like any other
OL,16,Ffamily trip to the Mediterranean. For
OL,17,Fthe first two days, the Kirbys soaked
OL,18,Fup the Greek sunshine, splashed in
OL,19,Fcrystal-clear waters, and created
OL,20,Fmemories across three generations. But
OL,21,Fon day three, everything changed.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G2/10
