OL,7,F"It started innocently enough`a
OL,8,Fmuscular pain down his side," recalls
OL,9,Fthe family. "We assumed it was from
OL,10,FAlan throwing the children into the
OL,11,Fsea all day at the beach. He'd been
OL,12,Fplaying with them for hours."
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G3/10
