OL,3,CHow a family fell foul of travel
OL,4,Cinsurance rules and now face a huge
OL,5,Cbill
OL,7,FWhat seemed like typical holiday
OL,8,Fmuscle strain quickly revealed itself
OL,9,Fas something far more sinister. The
OL,10,Fapparently healthy grandfather's
OL,11,Fcondition deteriorated rapidly, and
OL,12,Fwithin days he was diagnosed with
OL,13,Fpneumonia and suspected lung cancer,
OL,14,Fnow dependent on an oxygen tank to
OL,15,Fbreathe.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G4/10
