OL,7,FThe source of the Kirbys' nightmare
OL,8,Flies buried in the small print of
OL,9,Ftheir Allianz travel insurance policy.
OL,10,FAlan had failed to declare a benign
OL,11,Flung tumour discovered the previous
OL,12,Fyear`a condition that required no
OL,13,Factive treatment and seemed to have no
OL,14,Fimpact on his daily life.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G6/10
