OL,7,FTo Alan and his family, the inactive
OL,8,Ftumour appeared irrelevant to their
OL,9,Fholiday plans. To Allianz, however,
OL,10,Fthis omission was grounds to deny
OL,11,Fcoverage entirely, regardless of
OL,12,Fwhether the undisclosed condition was
OL,13,Fdirectly related to his current crisis.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G7/10
