OL,3,CHow a family fell foul of travel
OL,4,Cinsurance rules and now face a huge
OL,5,Cbill
OL,7,FIn a statement Allianz explained: "Our
OL,8,Fsympathies are with Mr Kirby and his
OL,9,Ffamily during his recovery. In common
OL,10,Fwith other travel insurers, we ask
OL,11,Fcustomers to adhere to policy terms,
OL,12,Fincluding disclosure of any pre-
OL,13,Fexisting medical conditions for anyone
OL,14,Fcovered under the policy.
OL,15,FUnfortunately, a pre-existing medical
OL,16,Fcondition was not disclosed to us, so
OL,17,Fwe are declining the claim. We acted
OL,18,Fin good faith and covered the costs of
OL,19,FMr Kirby until the pre-existing
OL,20,Fmedical condition was established."
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G8/10
