OL,7,FAs Alan fights for his life in Athens,
OL,8,Fhis families story has become a
OL,9,Fpowerful warning to travellers
OL,10,Feverywhere: when it comes to travel
OL,11,Finsurance, every medical detail
OL,12,Fmatters, no matter how insignificant
OL,13,Fit may appear.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}     G10/10
